18:53.500 --> 18:55.500
that are the media.

18:55.500 --> 18:57.500
And so I imagine...

18:57.500 --> 18:59.500
I think I was always interested in that stuff.

18:59.500 --> 19:01.500
And I was literally all my...

19:01.500 --> 19:04.500
Some of my friends now were my people who were...

19:04.500 --> 19:06.500
Like Woodward and Bernstein were big guys.

19:06.500 --> 19:09.500
And so I know the guys who knew them and stuff like that.

19:09.500 --> 19:11.500
I know a lot of journalists and that kind of thing.

19:11.500 --> 19:13.500
And that was an exciting idea.

19:13.500 --> 19:15.500
That here was the chorus.

19:15.500 --> 19:17.500
I don't know, it was an interesting device also.

19:17.500 --> 19:19.500
And it was cheap.

19:19.500 --> 19:21.500
You could do a lot of things without spending any money.

19:21.500 --> 19:23.500
It's the same as having a guy come out

19:23.500 --> 19:26.500
