20:16.500 --> 20:18.500
And I was like, I don't know why I was this way.

20:18.500 --> 20:19.500
I was 27 years old.

20:19.500 --> 20:21.500
I was like, no, that's terrible. You can't do that.

20:21.500 --> 20:23.500
We had a huge fight about it.

20:23.500 --> 20:24.500
Oh, really?

