E.T. is a robot, essentially.

01:30:04.500 --> 01:30:05.500
And I was really relieved.

01:30:05.500 --> 01:30:06.500
I was like, oh, thank God.

01:30:06.500 --> 01:30:07.500
This is so different from that.

01:30:07.500 --> 01:30:11.500
The stupid question, the gun holster that comes out of his leg,

