We didn't talk to him about it.

01:30:22.500 --> 01:30:24.500
He just said, oh, no, it has to be this way.

01:30:24.500 --> 01:30:25.500
And he just made that.

01:30:25.500 --> 01:30:27.500
He just myth-bustered it and said, fuck it,

01:30:27.500 --> 01:30:29.500
the thing comes out and I'm thinking of the gun.

01:30:29.500 --> 01:30:30.500
Of the many, many, many.

