The transformation where you go into death itself

01:31:46.500 --> 01:31:48.500
and then the only thing you're conscious of

01:31:48.500 --> 01:31:51.500
is the reassembly of your life.

01:31:51.500 --> 01:31:56.500
You, the audience, including a weird female executive

